{\mysystem} extracts counts and instances (entity-mentions) from the text segments to subsequently i) consolidate the counts to present the best answer, ii) present 
contextualization
as a means to semantically qualifying the predicted count, and iii) ground the count in instances. We denote the set of relevant text segments for a query by {{2209.07250_FO0001||FO}}.